com.tensegrity.palojava.http
Class ResponseParser

java.lang.Object
  com.tensegrity.palojava.http.ResponseParser

public class ResponseParser
extends java.lang.Object

Provides methods for parsing the CSV response from palo server. The parsing complies to csv data rules. For an overview of how to en- or decode comma separated values see e.g. http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comma-separated_values

parse

public static final java.lang.String[][] parse(java.lang.String response,
                                               char delim)
Parses the given string. The given string can contain more the one line. The regular expression ';[\r\n]' is used to determine the line end.

Parameters:
response - the response string from the palo server
delim - the values delimiter
